//- Support Page
extends layout

block content
  .container.mt-5.fade-in
    .row.justify-content-center
      .col-lg-8
        .card.shadow-lg.mb-4.animated-card
          .card-body
            h1.mb-3.text-primary.text-center Support
            p.lead.text-center.mb-4 If you have any questions, issues, or need help, please contact our support team below. Our dedicated representatives are committed to providing you with timely and effective support for all your inquiries. Whether you are facing technical difficulties, need assistance with your account, or simply have suggestions for improvement, we are here to listen and help. Our team strives to ensure that every customer receives a personalized and satisfactory experience.
            .row.mb-4
              .col-md-4.mb-3.mb-md-0
                .card.border-0.bg-light.text-center.py-3.animated-card
                  i.bi.bi-envelope-at-fill.display-5.text-primary.mb-2
                  h5 Email
                  p.mb-1
                    a(href="mailto:gulbano7060@gmail.com") gulbano7060@gmail.com
                  p.text-muted.small
                    | You can reach us via email 24/7. Our support staff will respond to your inquiry as soon as possible, typically within one business day. For urgent matters, please mention "URGENT" in your subject line to prioritize your request.
              .col-md-4.mb-3.mb-md-0
                .card.border-0.bg-light.text-center.py-3.animated-card
                  i.bi.bi-telephone-fill.display-5.text-success.mb-2
                  h5 Phone
                  p.mb-1 +92-349-4721836
                  p.text-muted.small
                    | Our phone support is available during working hours. Please have your account details ready for faster assistance. We value your time and aim to resolve your queries in the shortest time possible.
              .col-md-4
                .card.border-0.bg-light.text-center.py-3.animated-card
                  i.bi.bi-chat-dots-fill.display-5.text-info.mb-2
                  h5 Live Chat
                  p.mb-1 Available 9am - 6pm (Mon-Sat)
                  p.text-muted.small
                    | Use our live chat feature for instant help with common issues, order tracking, and quick troubleshooting. Our agents are trained to resolve most problems on the spot.
            hr
            h3.text-secondary.mt-4.mb-3 Support Hours
            ul.list-group.list-group-flush.mb-4
              li.list-group-item.d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center.bg-transparent
                span Monday - Saturday
                span 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM
              li.list-group-item.d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center.bg-transparent
                span Sunday
                span Closed
            p.text-muted.mt-2
              | Our support hours are designed to cover the majority of your needs throughout the week. During these hours, you can expect prompt responses from our team. If you contact us outside of these hours, we will get back to you as soon as possible on the next business day.
            h3.text-secondary.mt-4.mb-3 Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)
            .accordion#faqAccordion
              .accordion-item
                h2.accordion-header#faq1
                  button.accordion-button.collapsed(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#collapse1', aria-expanded='false', aria-controls='collapse1')
                    | How do I reset my password?
                .accordion-collapse.collapse#collapse1(aria-labelledby='faq1', data-bs-parent='#faqAccordion')
                  .accordion-body
                    | Visit the login page and click on 'Forgot Password'. Follow the instructions sent to your email. If you do not receive a reset email within a few minutes, please check your spam folder or contact our support team for further assistance. For your security, password reset links expire after 30 minutes.
              .accordion-item
                h2.accordion-header#faq2
                  button.accordion-button.collapsed(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#collapse2', aria-expanded='false', aria-controls='collapse2')
                    | How do I return a product?
                .accordion-collapse.collapse#collapse2(aria-labelledby='faq2', data-bs-parent='#faqAccordion')
                  .accordion-body
                    | Please refer to our Return Policy page for detailed instructions. Generally, you must ensure that the product is unused and in its original packaging. Our team will guide you through the process and provide you with a return authorization number. We strive to make returns as hassle-free as possible for our customers.
              .accordion-item
                h2.accordion-header#faq3
                  button.accordion-button.collapsed(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#collapse3', aria-expanded='false', aria-controls='collapse3')
                    | How do I contact support?
                .accordion-collapse.collapse#collapse3(aria-labelledby='faq3', data-bs-parent='#faqAccordion')
                  .accordion-body
                    | You can email, call, or use our live chat for assistance. For the fastest response, please include your order number or account details when contacting us. Our support staff is trained to handle a wide range of issues, from technical problems to billing inquiries.
            hr
            h3.text-secondary.mt-4.mb-3 Escalation Process
            p If your issue is not resolved within 48 hours, please escalate by emailing our supervisor at 
              a(href="mailto:supervisor@example.com") supervisor@example.com
            p.text-muted.small.mt-2
              | We take unresolved issues very seriously. Our escalation process ensures that your concern is reviewed by a senior member of our team, who will work closely with you until a satisfactory resolution is achieved. Please provide all relevant details and previous correspondence when escalating an issue.
            h3.text-secondary.mt-4.mb-2 Our Commitment
            p.mb-0 We are committed to providing you with the best customer service. Your satisfaction is our top priority. If you have suggestions or feedback, please let us know. We regularly review feedback to improve our services and products. Thank you for choosing us as your trusted provider.

